#Title
Capitalisation doesn't affect search result

#Description
On the main page of application capitalisation doesn't affect search result

#Pre-conditions
The application is installed

#Steps
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Type 'porto' into search field
4. Wait until search result is loaded
5. Save search result
6. Clean search field
7. Type 'PORTO' into search field
8. Wait until search result is loaded

#Expected result
Both search results contain the same cities